title: Hepta: Time Synchronization
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/time/hopf
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the status of the synchronization.

 This check supports Hepta 8029 and Hepta 8030 devices.

 If the device is synchronized via Radio with high precision, the state will be OK.
 If the device is synchronized via Radio with low precision, the state will be WARN.
 If the device synchronization is invalid or it is in mode Crystal, the state will be CRIT.

discovery:
 One service is created.

item:
 The fixed statement {{SyncModuleTimeSyncState}}
